Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛 這胸針真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,和花名很速配
